# 🤖 Machine Learning Project Ideas

Welcome to the **Machine Learning Project Ideas Repository** 🚀  
This repository contains a collection of innovative and real-world **Machine Learning Project Ideas** designed for learning, practice, research, and development.

These ideas help in improving problem-solving skills, understanding machine learning workflows, and building practical AI-based solutions across multiple domains.

