# 📂 Repository Structure

```bash
Machine-Learning-Project-Ideas/
│
├── datasets/
├── notebooks/
├── projects/
├── models/
├── images/
├── deployment/
├── requirements.txt
├── README.md
└── app.py
```

---

# ⚡ Installation

## 🔹 Clone Repository

```bash
git clone YOUR_REPOSITORY_URL
```

---

## 🔹 Navigate to Directory

```bash
cd Machine-Learning-Project-Ideas
```

---

## 🔹 Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

# ▶ Usage

```bash
python app.py
```

